msgctxt ""
"The placeholder is for the localized version of the iCal UID specification "
"link"
msgid ""
"Some events at the requested source are missing the UID attribute required by "
"the iCalendar Specification. One-Time and ICS File imports are allowed but "
"successive imports will create duplicated events on your site. Please contact "
"the source provider to fix the UID issue; linking them to %s may help them "
"more quickly resolve their feed's UID issue."
msgstr ""
"Alguns eventos na fonte solicitada faltam o atributo UID exigido pela "
"especificação iCalendar. Importações de arquivo único e ICS são permitidas, "
"mas as importações sucessivas criará eventos duplicados em seu site. Entre em "
"contato com o provedor de origem para corrigir o problema UID; vinculá-los a "
"%s pode ajudá-los a resolver mais rapidamente o problema de UID do feed."

